WEBVTT

00:06.460 --> 00:08.621
[theme music playing]

00:27.810 --> 00:30.028
[rock song playing]

00:32.150 --> 00:35.483
[Marcus] My whole life,
my father told me people will judge me.

00:35.910 --> 00:37.366
Justin, wake up.

00:37.450 --> 00:40.738
[Marcus] People will assume
they know who I am by looking at me.

00:40.950 --> 00:41.996
Justin, come on.

00:42.080 --> 00:45.072
We got to get you to Mrs. Baker
and the lawyers before court starts.

00:45.920 --> 00:48.036
[Marcus]
And that the deck is stacked against me.

00:48.130 --> 00:50.086
-Justin, get up! Come on.
-[Justin groans]

00:50.550 --> 00:51.369
[sighs]

00:52.260 --> 00:55.047
-I'm not so sure he got the message.
-It's disgusting.

00:55.970 --> 00:57.961
-He stinks.
-No, the clothes stink.

00:58.180 --> 01:00.000
He's been living on the street
for five months.

01:02.430 --> 01:03.727
[sighs]

01:05.140 --> 01:08.769
[Marcus] When you're faced with that,
when you're without power,

01:08.860 --> 01:11.818
