01:23.910 --> 01:26.652
-[Lainie] You're up early.
-Hi! Uh...

01:27.710 --> 01:28.779
Laundry. Yeah.

01:29.210 --> 01:33.328
-Is this new?
-Yes. It's, um, pre-distressed.

01:33.420 --> 01:35.797
-Clay, is that your gym clothes?
-Uh...

01:35.880 --> 01:38.371
-'Cause it smells--
-Yeah, um...

01:38.470 --> 01:41.598
I left them on the bathroom floor
last night, like I do,

01:41.680 --> 01:45.798
and you know,
at night, my aim isn't so good.

01:45.890 --> 01:46.879
[clicks tongue]

01:47.640 --> 01:49.767
Uh, your father had an early meeting,

01:49.850 --> 01:51.852
so it's just you and me
for breakfast, okay?

01:51.940 --> 01:53.931
Okay, great. Thanks, Mom.

01:56.070 --> 01:59.449
