To give in to the pain.

01:59.990 --> 02:02.197
Like Hannah did. She started to believe

02:02.280 --> 02:03.577
-that she was less than.
- [banging]

02:04.830 --> 02:05.649
Shit.

02:09.460 --> 02:11.530
[toilet flushing]

02:15.670 --> 02:16.830
Tony, it was heroin.

02:17.220 --> 02:20.041
I did, like, an image search
and it came up black tar heroin.

02:20.140 --> 02:21.846
He... He had heroin.

02:22.600 --> 02:25.888
[Marcus] To believe that a life
of privilege and position

02:26.560 --> 02:28.016
was only for other people.

02:29.770 --> 02:30.725
You're up early.

02:31.440 --> 02:33.852
You got Rodin coming over
for a yoga lesson?

02:34.480 --> 02:38.029
