in a position to make impossible choices.

07:54.760 --> 07:56.216
But it's not a fair system.

07:58.100 --> 08:00.421
And I want you
to look after yourself first.

08:02.850 --> 08:03.680
Yes, sir.

08:05.400 --> 08:07.265
You're gonna be great, okay?

08:09.280 --> 08:11.896
-[woman] Justice for Hannah!
-[indistinct clamoring]

08:11.990 --> 08:14.447
