and they heard you.

09:26.390 --> 09:27.266
[chuckles]

09:27.810 --> 09:28.845
[car door closing]

09:30.440 --> 09:32.146
-[Dennis] Good morning.
-Good morning.

09:33.150 --> 09:34.981
Your statement
had qUIte the Impact, clearly.

09:35.070 --> 09:37.026
-I knew you'd be upset.
-I'm not upset.

09:37.660 --> 09:40.026
They should hear from you
at the right time.

09:40.120 --> 09:42.862
People need to hear the whole story,
Hannah's story.

09:42.950 --> 09:45.783
-And they're not getting it in there.
-These kids are not on message.

09:45.870 --> 09:47.497
These kids are kids, Jackie.

09:47.580 --> 09:50.834
And they are the story.
We tell Hannah's story through them.

09:51.340 --> 09:53.296
-This Marcus Cole--
-Is a little politician.

09:53.920 --> 09:57.629
But he'd rather blame the school
than himself, and I can work with that.

09:57.970 --> 10:00.848
[Marcus]
When you're marginalized, powerless,

10:00.930 --> 10:02.557
you have to find strength somewhere.

10:03.350 --> 10:04.305
In friends.

10:04.390 --> 10:07.632
-Jess. Jessica.
-Hey, Clay, what's up?

10:08.940 --> 10:09.975
We have Justin.

10:11.440 --> 10:12.350
