Metcalf will let you slide.

11:11.250 --> 11:12.740
It's not a card, dude.

11:13.670 --> 11:17.083
No, I know. Fuck, sorry, brother.
You know what I mean.

11:17.170 --> 11:19.377
If Chle hadn't stopped
doing study group...

11:19.470 --> 11:22.428
I'm sorry, Zach.
I've just been so busy with everything.

11:22.680 --> 11:25.717
