I just need to get out of here.

16:57.850 --> 17:01.172
-Guys, I cannot skip this class.
-Zach, we need you!

17:02.310 --> 17:03.925
-You need my car.
-[Jessica] Both!

17:04.980 --> 17:08.893
Look, if we can't have you,
can we... maybe...

17:09.520 --> 17:14.139
-Okay, but only if Jess drives.
-It's an automatic. My right foot works.

17:15.280 --> 17:17.066
-Jess drives.
-Thank you, Zachy.

17:21.040 --> 17:22.029
[car revs]

17:23.000 --> 17:24.456
This car is so insane.

17:24.750 --> 17:27.287
Shouldn't we steal it
and do a road trIp across the country?

17:27.500 --> 17:29.991
Yes, running from the law,
like Thelma and Louise.

17:30.210 --> 17:32.542
Yeah, if Thelma had a bum leg
and boy parts.

17:32.630 --> 17:35.042
[giggles] It sounds so sew
when you say it like that.

17:35.130 --> 17:37.257
-I mean, I am pretty sexy.
-You totally are.

17:43.810 --> 17:45.971
I love the movies on a weekday.

17:46.060 --> 17:48.802
No lines. No waiting. No people.

17:48.900 --> 17:50.390
Wow, you're in a crazy good mood.

17:50.480 --> 17:54.223
-It's possible I'm just crazy.
-Well, I'm good either way.

17:55.240 --> 17:56.059
Hello!

18:00.530 --> 18:02.361
I haven't been to a movie in so long.

18:02.450 --> 18:04.156
-I'm having all the popcorn.
-[scoffs]

18:07.000 --> 18:09.457
So are you trying to have sex
with her now or something?

18:09.540 --> 18:12.953
_ What? No. _
Why Is that any of your busmess, anyway?

18:17.590 --> 18:18.545
[Jessica] Hey.

18:19.800 --> 18:22.758
-You okay?
-Yeah. I'm just tired.

18:23.510 --> 18:24.761
No, not just tired.

18:29.900 --> 18:31.219
That night that we came here,

18:31.480 --> 18:33.562
-and Hannah confronted me?
-Hmm.

18:33.860 --> 18:36.067
