being friends with her.

18:38.070 --> 18:41.119
-Yeah, but that's not your fault.
-Yeah, but I fucking lied, Jess.

18:41.410 --> 18:44.197
She was just hurt,
and then she called me out on it,

18:44.280 --> 18:47.659
